title: Callan Method 2015
description:
The Callan Method is a tried-and-tested direct method, used by millions of people across the world. First developed in the 1960s by Mr Robin Callan, it is an exceptionally quick way to successfully master English as a foreign language. 



The method is designed specifically to improve your listening and speaking abilities in a lively and active environment.

 
Start speaking English straight away with the Callan Method!
